    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Makashi Form:</strong> 3rd level</em></p>\n<p>You gain the following Channel the Force option.</p>\n<h3>Makashi Riposte</h3>\n<p>When another creature damages you with a melee attack, you can expend a use of your Channel the Force and use your reaction to attempt to deflect the attack. When you do so, the damage you take from the attack is reduced by [[/r 1d10]] + your Dexterity modifier + your guardian level.</p>\n<p>If you reduce the damage to 0, you can immediately make a single melee weapon attack against that creature as a part of the reaction.</p>",
